room_title: Escape room "The Red Wire" by PanIQ Room in San Francisco
room_description:
The intelligence world is cloaked in secret, but one of those secrets has slipped out. The Fixer, a shadowy foreign agent, has been identified by MI5 agents in London, and he is believed to be planning a terrorist attack here in the city.

Analysts have tracked him to an old neighborhood where he has established a safehouse. It is believed that he has completed building a bomb in preparation for his attack. You and your fellow agents have been assigned to find him and put a stop to his plans. Can you defuse this situation before it goes too far?
